{"tid":219039,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有得揀揀 你地會揀住係露營車定300尺貴到仆街的私樓","createTime":"2017-04-27T02:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T04:40:21.000Z","uid":101068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92ea2fd8aed1a4da2eafeb37a6d03325a993d9af","tid":219039,"uid":101068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"南昌站新盤匯璽以「焦點盤，驚喜價」作招徠，售價是毗鄰天璽呎價的三分一。最驚喜的莫過於一房戶最細單位只有270呎，焗爐夾在廁所與床頭之間，平均呎價$18,998。驚喜呎價與新盤，最近再次掀起網民熱熾討論香港居住露營車的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/104747_c08bb227f866864c767bddf1740464b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F104747_c08bb227f866864c767bddf1740464b7.jpg&h=59ec8a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有市民在三月初詢問運輸署，署方重申香港不能出牌給露營車。根據運輸署資料，現時擺放在個別地點的出租露營車不可在道路上行駛，亦不受《道路交通條例》規管。<br />\n<br />\n休閒露營車RV﹝Rreational Vehicle﹞在歐美國家流行已久，50年代的露營車更可以變身小船，上山下海乜都得。及至現在，美國樓價瘋狂飆升，興起住露營車過游牧生活的潮流。今年普萊森頓市大型露營車展覽上，Camping World RV銷售代理庫克（Sherri Cooke）表示，愈來愈多人考慮以露營車作為居所。以褔特的新款17 Freedom Elite30 FE為例，基本設計與匯璽相差無幾，1房1廳1廁所，豪裝程度靚過示範單位，售價約78萬港元。至於入門級的車款，約8萬美元，分分鐘平過香港新盤的首期。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/104837_6fdb2f1f038c8f35ce2a82e175156956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F104837_6fdb2f1f038c8f35ce2a82e175156956.jpg&h=9c6033a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民討論香港居住露營車的可能性，不少網民「眼光獨到」，指「你諗都唔駛諗，引入咗會影響香港樓價。試問嗰班幾層樓收租的高官點會咁X膠，畀機會引入呢」、「如果出到牌，香港樓價即冧﹝跌﹞5成」。香港政府應否出牌給露營車，甚至在停泊、行駛、土地問題上仍有待探討。"},{"pid":"dea7ecbc411045ea50ad1f2c6c25ce654782018f","tid":219039,"uid":101068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:53:46.000Z","msg":"露營車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bdc8cfc3f5f4878101803e9c2c5f17fede4527","tid":219039,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0660ea4933abac7b7b95c35da9fb5b493752a16","tid":219039,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:15:45.000Z","msg":"車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9d34bc51d8945121ae31753831643e50640313","tid":219039,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔係已經有人將架唔知咩車改裝完住入去啦咩？"},{"pid":"50b3ee58f2be6abbbca330f7b39ea16fa716ec1c","tid":219039,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:29:05.000Z","msg":"住貨倉同農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d176bc87eaf19dd78bdd914a80fef8e9d0eee5b3","tid":219039,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"香港係用黎搵錢既地方<br />\n你叫人搵少d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"548fa81e4f9ec5c006b563096844a6512dd8a3b0","tid":219039,"uid":107324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"偉大既祖國大把露營車周圍走，特區政府好應該效法。"}]}